## Installation automatisée

### Preseed (Debian/Ubuntu)

Fichier de configuration pour installation automatique. 

```bash
# Créer un fichier preseed
cat > preseed.cfg << 'EOF'
# Localization
d-i debian-installer/locale string fr_FR.UTF-8
d-i keyboard-configuration/xkb-keymap select fr

# Network
d-i netcfg/choose_interface select auto
d-i netcfg/get_hostname string ma-distro

# Mirror
d-i mirror/country string manual
d-i mirror/http/hostname string deb.debian.org
d-i mirror/http/directory string /debian

# Account
d-i passwd/user-fullname string Custom User
d-i passwd/username string customuser
d-i passwd/user-password password password123
d-i passwd/user-password-again password password123
d-i passwd/root-password password rootpass
d-i passwd/root-password-again password rootpass

# Partitioning
d-i partman-auto/method string regular
d-i partman-auto/choose_recipe select atomic
d-i partman/confirm_write_new_label boolean true
d-i partman/choose_partition select finish
d-i partman/confirm boolean true

# Packages
tasksel tasksel/first multiselect standard, xfce-desktop
d-i pkgsel/include string vim git htop

# GRUB
d-i grub-installer/only_debian boolean true
d-i grub-installer/bootdev string /dev/sda

# Finish
d-i finish-install/reboot_in_progress note
EOF
```

**Utilisation :**

```bash
# Au boot, passer le paramètre : 
auto=true url=http://server/preseed.cfg
```

### Kickstart (Fedora/RHEL)

```bash
# Exemple de kickstart
cat > kickstart.cfg << 'EOF'
#version=RHEL8
install
url --url="http://mirror.centos.org/centos/8/BaseOS/x86_64/os/"

lang fr_FR.UTF-8
keyboard fr
timezone Europe/Paris --utc

network --bootproto=dhcp --device=eth0 --onboot=yes

rootpw --plaintext password123
user --name=customuser --password=password123 --plaintext --groups=wheel

bootloader --location=mbr --boot-drive=sda

clearpart --all --drives=sda
autopart

%packages
@core
@base
@development
vim
git
%end

reboot
EOF
```

