## Tests et validation

### Vérifications de base

```bash
# Version du kernel
uname -r

# Version de la distribution
cat /etc/os-release

# Utilisation disque
df -h

# Utilisation mémoire
free -h

# Processus
ps aux | head

# Services actifs
systemctl list-units --type=service --state=running

# Logs système
journalctl -xe
```

### Tests matériels

```bash
# Informations CPU
lscpu

# Informations mémoire
sudo dmidecode --type memory

# Informations PCI (carte graphique, etc.)
lspci -v

# Tests de performance disque
sudo hdparm -tT /dev/sda

# Test de stress CPU
sudo apt install stress
stress --cpu 4 --timeout 60s
```

